==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Favorer
<hw>Fa"vor*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who favors; one
who regards with kindness or friendship; a well-wisher; one who assists
or promotes success or prosperity.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>favourer</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And come to us as <qex>favorers</qex>, not as foes.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Favoress</ent>⟦br⟧
